title: Ultimate Cheer & Dance NYC
desc: Join us in New York City for the Ultimate Cheer & Dance competition. Secure your team's place at the event today by registering for at least ten (10) team members and finalize the registration on or before November 30.*  The Event Schedule will be made available in early December. ? *Deposits made will reserve a spot in the competition for your team and cannot be refunded. We will make every effort to accommodate a transfer of the deposit amount to a future Ultimate Cheer & Dance event. Payment in full must be received by November 30, 2015. FAQs Where can I contact the organizer with any questions? Please contact cmarsh@madeventmanagement.com with any questions.? What are my transport/parking options getting to the event? The Javits Center is located on the far West Side of Mid-town Manhattan. It can be reached by car via the Lincoln or Holland Tunnels or the George Washington Bridge. There are many private parking garages in the area that charge prices that range from $30 - 60 per day. Please note that NYC parking garages often charge an extra fee for over-sized vehicles, including SUVs. Public transportation options include bus into Port Authority Bus Terminal at 42nd Street, Rail Service via Amtrak, New Jersey Transit, LIRR and Metro North.? PROUDLY SUPPORTED BY:
